---
// AboutPageGoogleReviews.astro — all 5 real Google reviews from screenshots
// Mobile: horizontal swipe, desktop: 3-col grid (first 3) + 2-col row (last 2)
---

<section class="google-reviews" aria-label="Google reviews">
