          <div class="gr-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="gr-quote">"When I first met Feldon, I hadn't yet started to take action towards my dreams. When I started receiving regular mentoring calls from him and being held accountable, it gave me that push to start taking action. I am surprised by how similar our experiences are as entrepreneurs."</p>
        </article>

