            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="gr-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="gr-quote">"I attended a marketing webinar with Feldon Haynes. It was very good and everything was explained really well, whether it was the content or answering my questions. My questions were answered well in depth and he ensured that I understood."</p>
        </article>

        <!-- 3. Rayaan Farah -->
        <article class="gr-card">
          <div class="gr-top">
            <div class="gr-avatar" style="background:#00897B">R</div>
            <div class="gr-info">
