            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="gr-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="gr-quote">"Feldon has been an incredible help to myself breaking down difficult policy language into understandable chunks, produced top quality policies for my organisation in a timely fashion and took the time to understand my pain points."</p>
        </article>

        <!-- 4. Kane Abbott -->
        <article class="gr-card">
          <div class="gr-top">
            <div class="gr-avatar" style="background:#7B1FA2">K</div>
            <div class="gr-info">
              <span class="gr-name">Kane Abbott</span>
              <span class="gr-meta">9 months ago</span>
            </div>
            <svg class="gr-glogo" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M22.56 12.25c0-.78-.07-1.53-.2-2.25H12v4.26h5.92c-.26 1.37-1.04 2.53-2.21 3.31v2.77h3.57c2.08-1.92 3.28-4.74 3.28-8.09z" fill="#4285F4"/>
              <path d="M12 23c2.97 0 5.46-.98 7.28-2.66l-3.57-2.77c-.98.66-2.23 1.06-3.71 1.06-2.86 0-5.29-1.93-6.16-4.53H2.18v2.84C3.99 20.53 7.7 23 12 23z" fill="#34A853"/>
              <path d="M5.84 14.09c-.22-.66-.35-1.36-.35-2.09s.13-1.43.35-2.09V7.07H2.18C1.43 8.55 1 10.22 1 12s.43 3.45 1.18 4.93l3.66-2.84z" fill="#FBBC05"/>
              <path d="M12 5.38c1.62 0 3.06.56 4.21 1.64l3.15-3.15C17.45 2.09 14.97 1 12 1 7.7 1 3.99 3.47 2.18 7.07l3.66 2.84c.87-2.6 3.3-4.53 6.16-4.53z" fill="#EA4335"/>
            </svg>
